244
00:24:23,703 --> 00:24:26,683
I heard you know the second son of Taekang Group well.

245
00:24:27,583 --> 00:24:29,383
Are you telling me to ask that bastard for help?

246
00:24:29,383 --> 00:24:32,753
You can tell him you'll pay him back when you win the competition.

247
00:24:32,753 --> 00:24:34,553
I'd rather sell my organs.

248
00:24:34,553 --> 00:24:37,923
He seems decent, being a CEO of a publishing company when he's already a conglomerate.

249
00:24:37,923 --> 00:24:39,923
