250
00:24:39,923 --> 00:24:41,863
Money and honor both.

251
00:24:41,863 --> 00:24:44,793
 Many people misunderstand like that. 

252
00:24:44,793 --> 00:24:48,383
"Isn't he trying to take over the publishing market when he's already a conglomerate?"

253
00:24:48,383 --> 00:24:50,943
