254
00:24:50,943 --> 00:24:55,023
"He'll go back to inherit the family business in the end," and so on.

255
00:24:55,023 --> 00:24:59,483
I know well that many people have an unkind opinion of me.

256
00:24:59,483 --> 00:25:01,643
It is a little unfair.

257
00:25:01,643 --> 00:25:08,063
Because I'm just a person... who likes to read books...

258
00:25:08,063 --> 00:25:12,133
write literature, and hold debates with my friends.

259
00:25:12,133 --> 00:25:16,393
In short, I guess you can say I'm crazy about books.

260
00:25:16,393 --> 00:25:19,603
A mansion? My publishing company is?

261
00:25:19,603 --> 00:25:22,663
